    {
      "instruction": "<p>Put a large baking tray (or two) in the oven to heat up (this will stop your pizza bottom[s] from going soggy!)</p><p>Add your <strong>tomato paste </strong>to a bowl with your <strong>BBQ sauce</strong> and 5 tbsp<span class=\"text-purple\"> [7 1/2 tbsp]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [10 tbsp]</span> <strong>cold water</strong></p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong> and stir it all together – this is your <strong>BBQ base</strong></p>",
