    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>BBQ pulled pork</strong> to a clean chopping board and chop into small bite-sized pieces</p><p>Transfer the <strong>chopped BBQ pork</strong> to a bowl with the <strong>juices</strong> and mix it all together – this is your <strong>BBQ pork</strong></p>",
