    {
      "instruction": "<p>Remove the heated tray[s] from the oven and add your <strong>pizza base[s]</strong></p><p>Divide the <strong>BBQ base</strong> between the <strong>pizza base[s]</strong> and spread it evenly all over with the back of a spoon, then top with the <strong>BBQ pork</strong></p><p>Top with the <strong>torn mozzarella </strong>and put the tray[s] in the oven for 12-15 min or until the cheese has melted and the base is crispy – this is your <strong>BBQ pork pizza[s]</strong></p>",
